As the national Local Government Association we represent the interest of all 341 Local Councils in Sri Lanka, in this regard we are linked to the Mayors and Commissioners (Civil Servants) all the councils. &#xd;
We are working in collaboration with the National Ministry of Local Govt. and Provincial Ministries of Local Govt. &#xd;
FSLGA facilitates Mayors Caucuses, Women Councilors Caucus and Local Council Chief Executive (Civil Servants) Network.
